<h2 class="wprm-recipe-name wprm-block-text-bold">Creamy Garlic Chicken</h2>
<div class="wprm-spacer" style="height: 5px;"></div>
<div class="wprm-recipe-summary wprm-block-text-normal"><span style="display: block;">This <em><strong>one pot creamy garlic chicken</strong></em> is made with parmesan, garlic and cilantro (or herb of choice) for a delicious 20 minute meal. All you have to do is throw everything in one skillet or pot and once cooked, you can taste the fragrant flavor. The juicy chicken thighs go great with white rice and side of veggies.</span></div>
<div class="wprm-spacer"></div>
